Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狮堂光\N龙啸海、凤凰寺风三人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被艾美诺公主召唤成为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.47,0:01:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救异世界锡菲罗的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到魔神些列斯的光等人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续旅程找寻余下的两部魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,途中 她们被发光魔物袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海和风被捉去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光独自迎抗来历不明的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光想着三人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为魔法骑士的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.43,0:02:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.97,0:02:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二部魔神·空神温达姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事?伊诺巴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰殿下休息 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些魔法骑士即将到达
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温达姆沉睡的风之神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下 请你批准我去打倒她们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱尔希欧蕾、阿斯克特和
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔汀娜也已经被击败
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你允许我去魔法骑士那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊诺巴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会讨伐魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来这里向你报告
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了实现殿下你的真正心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你批准我去魔法骑士那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我失言了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我的意图却跟着我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害的风暴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好有个山洞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风 站在那里会被雨淋湿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这里啊 小风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事呢?刚才还那么好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是\N锡菲罗正在崩溃的证明吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要只是说不吉利的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 古列夫也说过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗全年都天朗气清呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫最近没和我们通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不可以死在这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风 你听到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风 风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧?如今在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身处一望无际的好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不能说没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风好大 有点不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我和你们会合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道 我们正在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之神殿下的山洞里避风雨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你要平安无事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道 谢谢你 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何喜形于色呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作 振作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草药…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草药?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧也看来退了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没大碍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她晕倒在路旁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何追着我们啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了和亲爱的风见面…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我有事想告诉你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草药…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草药在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心 我已经帮你捡齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫西娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我住在山脚的衬里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为弟弟突然发高烧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我来摘草药
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后突然下雨 我不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有各位我就不知怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是谢谢你们救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别客气…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好菲力欧路过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风暴停止前 我们在这里等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风暴…吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风暴就是刮着大风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷电交加 中心有风眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四周被黑云包围 巨响连连
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那么厉害的魔物吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗没风暴的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从未见过这么差的天气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫最近有联络来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗由和平时起已经有魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但想不到连天气也坏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两三日\N锡菲罗突然开始崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且以非常快的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们快点\N锡菲罗已经时日无多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是来把那件事告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经日落 在风暴停止前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家休息比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不睡看着外面的情形啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想看清楚罕见的风暴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲… 西娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:09:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?睡不着吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点害怕…\N锡菲罗真的在崩溃?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝了汤 身子暖和后便不会感到害怕的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.46,0:09:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 请你试用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和草药一起摘回来的香草
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我尝尝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很美味呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 稍为当作谢礼了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能喝上这么美味的汤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少次我也会救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真会说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家看啊 风暴停了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 睡着了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧 振作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高烧得很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是昨天的雨的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把菲力欧先生交给我照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为各位有要赶快完成的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 小风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何一直板起脸孔啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住…不要想多余的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想着拯救锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定能拯救锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:11:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会取得魔神回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西娜小姐 菲力欧拜托你照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟…怎么了…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体…\N完全不听使唤…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧先生和风小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被强大的感情连在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见那位风小姐在眼前死去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.18,0:11:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会有何感觉呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别香草的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图的手下吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全靠你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道其中一位魔法骑士的弱点了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就被绑在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢看着魔法骑士的死期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着叫风的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一面叫着亲爱的你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一面死去的模样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然有飞行工具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何不快点拿出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到谢加图\N的攻击后好像有不妥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风? 小风?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在呼唤我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔神在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消…消失了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海你找到魔神瑟列斯时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.42,0:13:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是发呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的魔神一定在呼唤小风
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了 魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:14:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不像是来欢迎我们的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.68,0:14:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白费气力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的魔法骑士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到这神殿驾御我的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是温达姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是等待成为\N魔法骑士的人到来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在这里沉睡的魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.01,0:14:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是魔神?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只巨大的鸟…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来驾御我的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展示你心的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展示你有资格驾御我的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展示你有资格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为魔法骑士的心的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你振作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护不了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无还手之力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不堪一击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫伊诺巴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉谢加图殿下之命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前来消灭魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟敢伤害小光和小海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.09,0:15:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑…无效?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该说过…这是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这么轻易就能收拾你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本就不需要人质
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.01,0:16:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人质?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个糊涂小子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出所料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看来对这个男人有特别感情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出所料?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何认识菲力欧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西娜小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风 若你如今\N在这里跪在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发誓不做魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就饶这个男人一命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见他你不心痛吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能撕开这个男人的身体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说 说你不做魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他知道\N我向你屈服他才得救
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也不会高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 小光和小海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来\N和我一起努力上路…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我抛下舍身保护
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和魔神对话的我的同伴而独善其身…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你打算怎样?魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒你 拯救菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说的魔法骑士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我承认你强力的心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔神…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就从沉睡中苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展示我的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…魔神?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护甲…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护甲在成长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.77,0:18:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑也成长了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三个人都成长了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说的魔法骑士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还未是时候驾御我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在要来的日子来临前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会改变形态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为你的一部份
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在暂时等一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直至要来的日子来临
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的已经没事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…\N决定不再在你面前出现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会妨碍你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有菲力欧你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才能打倒伊诺巴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才能唤醒魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候 我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…不能原谅自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想着我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.69,0:20:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想着拯救锡菲罗这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们一定做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气死人了 不听别人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我突然流泪…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泪停不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风 你真的想忘记菲力欧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 不要忘记他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直想着他就行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的事绝对不是菲力欧的错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想见他 消除误会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 只要努力祈求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定能和菲力欧见面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相谅解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里是意志的世界锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呢 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因这这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有信念的心\N会成为力量的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 谢加图大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我求你 请你把我变回原形
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.62,0:22:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来吧 拉法格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:10.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:21.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:29.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:37.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,海的颜色逐渐染成红色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:39.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,无重力状态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:44.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,想就此被风带走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然以不认输的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:53.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,跳过经常跳不过的栏杆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:01:02.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,但用不完的实力是谁所赐?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:09.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着停不了的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:15.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧不能转让的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:20.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,心底不褪色的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:25.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,背着阳光透出耀眼光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:39.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,面带最美的笑容用力踏脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:46.59,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,逆风也不可以沮丧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:52.49,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不输给悲伤的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.53,0:22:59.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,悄悄地告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.13,0:23:04.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着广阔海洋前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:11.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 你的瞳孔终有一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:17.12,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,会在阳光下散发光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.15,0:23:24.46,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不要灰心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.49,0:23:29.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,把信念化成奔向明日的勇气
